# Vietnamese translation for Powerbuilder UI.
# DRAFT — flagged for native-speaker review before any production rollout.
# Translator notes: register is informal-respectful, suitable for community
# organizing (use "bạn" for the user; avoid overly formal "quý vị" outside
# of formal mailers). Tone is warm and direct. Vietnamese organizing-tone
# formality registers vary by region and generation, so this draft MUST be
# reviewed by a native speaker familiar with the target community
# (Vietnamese American voters in Gwinnett County / GA-07) before launch.
# Do NOT translate proper nouns: Powerbuilder, OpenAI, Pinecone, Census
# API, FEC, Gwinnett, Beta.
#
